creator: zhuxiao79@126.com
text:
ERROR on maven building:
The following artifacts could not be resolved: commons-math3:commons-math3:jar:3.4.1, commons-pool2:commons-pool2:jar:2.3

Cause wrong groupId settings in "ApacheJMeter_parent-2.13.pom" (http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/apache/jmeter/ApacheJMeter_parent/2.13/ApacheJMeter_parent-2.13.pom) :

Artifact "commons-math3" and "commons-pool2" have the wrong groupId, which should be "org.apache.commons"
